- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as machine translation is a subfield of AI.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions the use of BLEU scores, which are commonly used in evaluating information retrieval systems.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the least likely category as the paper does not focus on image or video processing, which are the main topics of computer vision.
